name: First Pentacle of Luna[PentacleCoin]
description: The PentacleCoin! The Pentacles of Solomon are planetary seals which were made by King Solomon for magickal purpose. Every of the Ancient Planets got 7 Pentacles. The perfect Collectible for Magick, Mystery & Mythology Fans! The Second Coin of the PentacleCoin Series is the FIRST PENTACLE OF LUNA "It serves to call forth and invoke the Spirits of the Moon; and it further serveth to open doors, inwhatever way they may be fastened."
